{"tid":2250291,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"特朗普批評福奇為「災難」、「蠢材」 (11:04)","createTime":"2020-10-20T04:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T08:23:03.000Z","uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"15d7c39070cdc869dffbf361fc2f746bc3ca1007","tid":2250291,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:11:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20201020/s00005/1603158169282/特朗普批福奇為「災難」-「蠢材」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20201020%2Fs00005%2F1603158169282%2F%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%89%B9%E7%A6%8F%E5%A5%87%E7%82%BA%E3%80%8C%E7%81%BD%E9%9B%A3%E3%80%8D-%E3%80%8C%E8%A0%A2%E6%9D%90%E3%80%8D&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEeDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=283bb1dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20201020%2Fs00005%2F1603158169282%2F%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%89%B9%E7%A6%8F%E5%A5%87%E7%82%BA%E3%80%8C%E7%81%BD%E9%9B%A3%E3%80%8D-%E3%80%8C%E8%A0%A2%E6%9D%90%E3%80%8D&h=072e0022\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20201020/s00005/1603158169282/特朗普批福奇為「災難」-「蠢材」</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020/10/20<br />\n<br />\n美國國立過敏與傳染病研究院總監福奇（Anthony Fauci），一直被視為是美國對抗新型冠狀病毒的抗疫大將，惟美國總統特朗普矛盾頗深。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普周一（19日）在與競選團隊的電話會議中，形容福奇是「災難」和「蠢材」，每次福奇上電視「總會有炸彈」，但如開除他「炸彈就會更大」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特朗普亦稱，人們已受夠了新冠病毒，「聽厭了福奇和所有這些蠢材（意指其他衛生官員）的說話」。特朗普更說，如果由福奇主持抗疫工作，美國將有50萬人死於新型冠狀病毒。"},{"pid":"bd64dd2aebb81aba6bcc28d043126f95d611dfc1","tid":2250291,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:12:45.000Z","msg":"侵侵終於忍夠了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bacca3a77a5c2055cd1045dbd6857eb07db5b8c2","tid":2250291,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />恐懼撚又嬴<b